<s1 id=ChangeBackdropTA> To Select a Backdrop
 
        <idx|backdrop: selecting|
        <idx|selecting: backdrop|
 
<list order>
 
* Switch to the workspace in which you want the backdrop.
 
* Click the Style Manager Backdrop control.
 
* Select a backdrop.
 
* Click Apply.
 
<\list>
 
        <idx|dialog box: Backdrop|
        <idx|Backdrop dialog box|
 
<!-- <figure nonumber entity=BackdropDialogBox>
<\figure> -->
 
A backdrop is a pattern that covers the workspace (the screen area
underneath your windows).  
 
 
