<s1 id=ChangeMouseTA> To Change Mouse Orientation
 
        <idx|customizing: mouse orientation|
        <idx|mouse: customizing orientation|
        <idx|Mouse dialog box|
        <idx|dialog box: Mouse|
 
 
<list order>
 
* Click the Style Manager Mouse control.
 
* Select the Right or Left check box.
  This will reverse mouse buttons 1 and 3.
 
* Click OK.
 
