 <s1 id=ChangeMouseB2TA>To Change Mouse Button 2 Behavior
 
        <idx|customizing: mouse button 2 behavior|
        <idx|mouse: customizing button 2 behavior|
        <idx|Mouse dialog box|
        <idx|dialog box: Mouse|
 
<list order>
 
* Click the Style Manager Mouse control.
 
* Select the Transfer or Adjust check box to associate that
  action with mouse button 2.
   
* Click OK.
 
<\list>
 
<note>
On a two-button mouse the above does not apply.
<\note>

