        <idx|dialog box: Mouse|
 

<list order>
 
* Click the Style Manager Mouse control.
 
* Adjust the Double-Click gauge to set the maximum amount of time between
  single clicks to be considered a double-click.
 
* Click OK.
 
<\list>
 
